    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Godetia bifrons are skin irritations, which are effectively treated with its anti-inflammatory properties, reducing redness and swelling. This plant is also used to alleviate fever, as its flavonoids have been shown to inhibit the replication of certain pathogens. Additionally, Godetia bifrons is employed to soothe digestive issues, such as diarrhea and stomach cramps, by reducing inflammation in the gastrointestinal tract. Furthermore, its antiseptic properties make it an effective remedy for wound infections, preventing the growth of bacteria and promoting healing. By reducing inflammation and promoting healing, Godetia bifrons also helps to alleviate joint pain and inflammation, making it a valuable treatment for arthritis.",
